": [944.3, 811.5, 986.5, 830.2]}, {"text": "$ 1.0", "bbox": [1007.3, 811.5, 1049.5, 830.2]}, {"text": "$ 0.4", "bbox": [1070.3, 811.5, 1112.5, 830.2]}, {"text": "The asset allocation for our U.S. pension plan, and the target asset allocation for 2006, by asset category, is shown", "bbox": [204.2, 853.9, 1112.3, 874.7]}, {"text": "in the table below. The fair value of plan assets for our U.S. qualified pension plan was $832.0 million and $738.7", "bbox": [162.5, 878.9, 1112.4, 899.7]}, {"text": "million, at December 31, 2006 and December 31, 2005, respectively. The expected long-term rate of return on these", "bbox": [162.5, 903.9, 1112.4, 924.7]}, {"text": "plan assets was 8.75 percent for 2006 and 2005. In developing the assumption for the long-term rate of return on assets", "bbox": [162.5, 928.9, 1112.4, 949.7]}, {"text": "for our plan, we take into consideration the technical analysis performed by our outside actuaries, including historical", "bbox": [162.5, 953.9, 1112.4, 974.7]}, {"text": "market returns, information on the assumption for long-term real returns by asset class, inflation assumptions, and", "bbox": [162.5, 978.9, 1112.5, 999.7]}, {"text": "expectations for standard deviation related to these best estimates. We also consider the historical performance of our", "bbox": [162.5, 1003.9, 1112.5, 1024.7]}, {"text": "own plan’s trust, which has earned a compound annual rate of return of approximately 12 percent over the last 10 years", "bbox": [162.5, 1028.9, 1112.4, 1049.7]}, {"text": "(which is in excess of comparable market indices for the same period) as well as other factors. Given an actively", "bbox": [162.5, 1053.9, 1112.6, 1074.7]}, {"text": "managed investment portfolio, the expected annual rates of return by asset class for our portfolio, using geometric", "bbox": [162.5, 1078.9, 1112.6, 1099.7]}, {"text": "averaging, and after being adjusted for an estimated inflation rate of approximately 3 percent, is between 9 percent and", "bbox": [162.5, 1103.9, 1112.3, 1124.7]}, {"text": "11 percent for both U.S. and non-U.S. equities, and between 5 percent and 7 percent for fixed-income investments,", "bbox": [162.5, 1128.9, 1112.4, 1149.7]}, {"text": "which generates a total expected portfolio return that is in line with our assumption for the rate of return on assets.", "bbox": [162.5, 1153.9, 1067.2, 1174.7]}, {"text": "Percentage of Plan Assets", "bbox": [778.0, 1180.0, 959.9, 1196.7]}, {"text": "December 31,", "bbox": [820.3, 1196.7, 917.5, 1213.3]}, {"text": "Asset Category", "bbox": [235.5, 1221.7, 343.3, 1238.3]}, {"text": "Target Asset Allocation", "bbox": [437.2, 1221.7, 604.7, 1238.3]}, {"text": "2006", "bbox": [725.2, 1221.7, 758.5, 1238.3]}, {"text": "2005", "bbox": [979.2, 1221.7, 1012.5, 1238.3]}, {"text": "Equity securities . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [162.5, 1249.4, 416.4, 1268.2]}, {"text": "80 – 85%", "bbox": [485.0, 1249.4, 556.9, 1268.2]}, {"text": "79.4%", "bbox": [722.4, 1249.4, 770.8, 1268.2]}, {"text": "74.0%", "bbox": [976.4, 1249.4, 1024.8, 1268.2]}, {"text": "Fixed income investments . . . . . .", "bbox": [162.5, 1270.2, 416.4, 1289.0]}, {"text": "15 – 25%", "bbox": [485.0, 1270.2, 556.9, 1289.0]}, {"text": "18.0%", "bbox": [722.4, 1270.2, 770.8, 1289.0]}, {"text": "22.4%", "bbox": [976.4, 1270.2, 1024.8, 1289.0]}, {"text": "Cash and other short-term", "bbox": [162.5, 1291.1, 357.8, 1309.8]}, {"text": "investments . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [181.3, 1311.9, 416.4, 1330.7]}, {"text": "0 – 5%", "bbox": [494.4, 1311.9, 547.5, 1330.7]}, {"text": "2.6%", "bbox": [731.8, 1311.9, 770.8, 1330.7]}, {"text": "3.6%", "bbox": [985.7, 1311.9, 1024.8, 1330.7]}, {"text": "Total . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [200.0, 1341.1, 416.4, 1359.8]}, {"text": "100.0%", "bbox": [713.0, 1341.1, 770.8, 1359.8]}, {"text": "100.0%", "bbox": [967.0, 1341.1, 1024.8, 1359.8]}, {"text": "The fair value of plan assets for our foreign pension plans totaled $54.8 million and $31.1 mill